name: Create Qualtrics directory contacts from new Google Sheets spreadsheet rows
description: Make will watch for new rows in a specified Google Sheets spreadsheet at regular intervals and create directory contacts in Qualtrics. The template uses this [example spreadsheet](https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1fZLk6wYKUUEUuITboFmxFvP2cqEQ2ikkPsHOCHp8Nj4/edit?usp=sharing).
